<paragraph blockId="4.[813,1418,532,1081]" pageId="4" pageNumber="3194">Diagnostic characters: Posterior margin of female subgenital plate almost straight and smooth. Male supra anal plate with a tubercles on each side of median apical process, cercus laterally much compressed and of uniform width.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[813,1418,532,1081]" pageId="4" pageNumber="3194">
