, 
<date box="[1179,1301,756,782]" pageId="4" pageNumber="3194" value="2010-11-20">20.xi.2010</date>
, on paddy, Araria.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[813,1418,532,1081]" pageId="4" pageNumber="3194">Morphometry: (length in mm). Female: Body 14.7, Tegmina 22.8, Hind femur 14.2, Pronotum 8.8.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[813,1418,532,1081]" pageId="4" pageNumber="3194">Remarks: Pest of Paddy but also found in grasslands.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[813,1418,532,1081]" box="[850,1378,980,1007]" pageId="4" pageNumber="3194">Natural enemies: No natural enemies recorded.</paragraph>
